elinunte: edizione e commento",[273,274,275,276,277,278,279],"VC9IHZAR","IEFIMGIK","7UQBFBPB","RWXNUFEX","N5IF2DZR","F2GG87EQ","SEW88NC7",[281,281,282,25,32,36,283,284,285,286,287,288,289,129],"isic030010",{"_":4},"selinus","selinunte","sicilia","sicily","palermo","museo archeologico regionale antonino salinas","ancient greek",[],{"title":292,"body":293,"divs":294,"editions":321,"images":331,"handnote":337},"ISic030010. ISic030010","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">Χάμις\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐπέχ̣ο̄ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>κα&lt;ὶ&gt; νόσο̄ ῥοπᾶι \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἐπ’ ἀτελείαι ℎο-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>τ̣[ι] ΚΑ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span>]Ε̣[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span>]Ο̣ΝΤΙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">ΧΑΜΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΠΕ.Ο̄\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΚΑΝΟΣΟ̄ΡΟΠΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΕΠΑΤΕΛΕΙΑΙℎΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>.[.]ΚΑ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··\u003C/span>].[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··\u003C/span>].ΝΤΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030010_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030010_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030010.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030010-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Bettarini\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Je te maintiens dans la crise fatale de la maladie afin que tu ne puisses atteindre tes objectifs.(Dubois)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Chamis ti conduco alla fase critica della malattia perché tu non possa portare a termine ...\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Il doit s'agir d'une imprécation contre un grabataire dont l'impotence réjouit le rédacteur de la tablette. (Dubois)\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>A pesar de su brevedad, èste es uno de los documentos que demuestra un estilo màas refinado, con una figura insòlita como es la metáfora, y un verbo también inusual, ἐπέχω, que hacen de ella una de las defixiones de mayor originalidad. (Lopez-Jimeno)\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Questa lamina ci offre l'occasione di rivedere l'abusato cliché che vuole le defixiones redatte unicamente secondo formule stereotipe. Il problema interpretativo riguarda le prime due linee, dove a una sequenza iniziale certamente di tipo onomastico segue il verbo επεχω - un unicum nelle maledizioni - e la singolare espressione νόσου ῥοπα. Pare evidente quindi che la volontà di chi ha inciso la lamina è di condurre (επεχω) il defisso alla \"fase critica della malattia\", evidentemente per procurarne la morte. (Bettarini)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 26.0111 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 1976 81-83, no. 4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002280\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002280\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Jordan 1985 175, no. 97 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001391\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001391\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1989 no. 66 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">32\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> López-Jimeno 1991 no. 7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001858\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001858\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bettarini 2005 87-90, no. 17 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Curbera 1999 178, no. 20 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002060\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002060\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1-4  3.5   \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[295,298,301,304,307,309,312,315,318],{"id":296,"html":297},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">Χάμις\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐπέχ̣ο̄ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>κα&lt;ὶ&gt; νόσο̄ ῥοπᾶι \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἐπ’ ἀτελείαι ℎο-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>τ̣[ι] ΚΑ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span>]Ε̣[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span>]Ο̣ΝΤΙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Savannah Neibart\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">ΧΑΜΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΕΠΕ.Ο̄\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΚΑΝΟΣΟ̄ΡΟΠΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΕΠΑΤΕΛΕΙΑΙℎΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>.[.]ΚΑ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··\u003C/span>].[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··\u003C/span>].ΝΤΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":299,"html":300},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030010_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030010_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030010.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030010-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":302,"html":303},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Bettarini\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":305,"html":306},"translation","\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Je te maintiens dans la crise fatale de la maladie afin que tu ne puisses atteindre tes objectifs.(Dubois)\u003C/p>  ",{"id":305,"html":308},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Chamis ti conduco alla fase critica della malattia perché tu non possa portare a termine ...\u003C/p>  ",{"id":310,"html":311},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Il doit s'agir d'une imprécation contre un grabataire dont l'impotence réjouit le rédacteur de la tablette. (Dubois)\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>A pesar de su brevedad, èste es uno de los documentos que demuestra un estilo màas refinado, con una figura insòlita como es la metáfora, y un verbo también inusual, ἐπέχω, que hacen de ella una de las defixiones de mayor originalidad. (Lopez-Jimeno)\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Questa lamina ci offre l'occasione di rivedere l'abusato cliché che vuole le defixiones redatte unicamente secondo formule stereotipe. Il problema interpretativo riguarda le prime due linee, dove a una sequenza iniziale certamente di tipo onomastico segue il verbo επεχω - un unicum nelle maledizioni - e la singolare espressione νόσου ῥοπα. Pare evidente quindi che la volontà di chi ha inciso la lamina è di condurre (επεχω) il defisso alla \"fase critica della malattia\", evidentemente per procurarne la morte. (Bettarini)\u003C/p>  ",{"id":313,"html":314},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 26.0111 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 1976 81-83, no. 4 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002280\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002280\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Jordan 1985 175, no. 97 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001391\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001391\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1989 no. 66 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">32\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> López-Jimeno 1991 no. 7 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001858\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001858\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Bettarini 2005 87-90, no. 17 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001388\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Curbera 1999 178, no. 20 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002060\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002060\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":316,"html":317},"handnote","  Line 1-4  3.5   ",{"id":319,"html":320},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[322,324,327,328],{"html":323},"Text encoding: Savannah Neibart",{"id":325,"lang":129,"html":326},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"idionym\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">Χάμις\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἐπέχ̣ο̄ \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>κα&lt;ὶ&gt; νόσο̄ ῥοπᾶι \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ἐπ’ ἀτελείαι ℎο-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>τ̣[ι] ΚΑ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span>]Ε̣[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..\u003C/span>]Ο̣ΝΤΙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":323},{"id":329,"lang":129,"html":330},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Χάμις\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-